{"tid":2067028,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"食品史上的6月16日：23年就等這一天！台灣正式從「口蹄疫疫區」除名！","createTime":"2020-06-16T16:54:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T17:52:06.000Z","uid":254183,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3589cb78279e6a2752d6455c13c6a91755b60440","tid":2067028,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T16:54:50.000Z","msg":"等了23年，台灣終於正式告別「口蹄疫疫區」的身分了！2020年6月16日，世界動物衛生組織（World Organisation for Animal Health，簡稱OIE）正式通知台灣改列為「口蹄疫非疫區」，自1997年口蹄疫在台爆發以來，台灣歷經23年，終於從「疫區」轉變為「打針的非疫區」、再到如今的「不用打針的非疫區」，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">與日本一同成為「亞洲唯二不用打疫苗的非疫區」</span></strong>，也象徵台灣終於擺脫口蹄疫這個糾纏多年的惡夢！<br />\n<br />\n從口蹄疫除名，不僅可讓台灣每年節省3億元防治口蹄疫的疫苗費用與人力支出，更讓台灣的生鮮豬肉能風光外銷、重返國際。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.foodnext.net/column/columnist/paper/5852335740\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foodnext.net%2Fcolumn%2Fcolumnist%2Fpaper%2F5852335740&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG94xWyFD0xakOW3kliQQxS8%3D&h=2d8ee3af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.foodnext.net/column/columnist/paper/5852335740</a>"},{"pid":"d80690228b9940c39275ec9ebf4a33f9616941bd","tid":2067028,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T16:56:07.000Z","msg":"全文source<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.foodnext.net/column/columnist/paper/5852466347\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foodnext.net%2Fcolumn%2Fcolumnist%2Fpaper%2F5852466347&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG94xWyFD0xakOW3kliQQxS8%3D&h=491bcf8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.foodnext.net/column/columnist/paper/5852466347</a>"},{"pid":"d1d2bea346cfd16d68c73fd324ca4b9ae40d1886","tid":2067028,"uid":6030,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T16:56:46.000Z","msg":"japan no.1<br />\ntaiwan no.2"},{"pid":"d42b7de517c14affbea7daf67100473168ef2e61","tid":2067028,"uid":13678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T16:58:43.000Z","msg":"好在頂到隔離啲豬瘟恐襲<img src=\